016package org.lifstools.jmzqc;
017
018import com.fasterxml.jackson.core.*;
019import com.fasterxml.jackson.core.type.*;
020import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.*;
021import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.*;
022import java.io.IOException;
023import java.util.Collections;
024import java.util.List;
025import java.util.Objects;
026
027/**
028 * One or more controlled vocabulary elements describing the unit of the metric.
029 */
030@JsonDeserialize(using = Unit.Deserializer.class)
031@JsonSerialize(using = Unit.Serializer.class)
032public class Unit {
033
034    public CvParameter cvParameterValue;
035    public List<CvParameter> cvParameterArrayValue;// = Collections.emptyList();
036
037    public Unit() {
038    }
039
040    public Unit(CvParameter cvParameterValue, List<CvParameter> cvParameterArrayValue) {
041        this.cvParameterValue = cvParameterValue;
042        this.cvParameterArrayValue = cvParameterArrayValue;
043    }
044
045    public CvParameter getCvParameterValue() {
046        return cvParameterValue;
047    }
048
049    public void setCvParameterValue(CvParameter cvParameterValue) {
050        this.cvParameterValue = cvParameterValue;
051    }
052
053    public List<CvParameter> getCvParameterArrayValue() {
054        return cvParameterArrayValue;
055    }
056
057    public void setCvParameterArrayValue(List<CvParameter> cvParameterArrayValue) {
058        this.cvParameterArrayValue = cvParameterArrayValue;
059    }
060
061    @Override
062    public int hashCode() {
063        int hash = 7;
064        hash = 71 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.cvParameterValue);
065        hash = 71 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.cvParameterArrayValue);
066        return hash;
067    }
068
069    @Override
070    public boolean equals(Object obj) {
071        if (this == obj) {
072            return true;
073        }
074        if (obj == null) {
075            return false;
076        }
077        if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {
078            return false;
079        }
080        final Unit other = (Unit) obj;
081        if (!Objects.equals(this.cvParameterValue, other.cvParameterValue)) {
082            return false;
083        }
084        return Objects.equals(this.cvParameterArrayValue, other.cvParameterArrayValue);
085    }
086
087    static class Deserializer extends JsonDeserializer<Unit> {
088
089        @Override
090        public Unit deserialize(JsonParser jsonParser, DeserializationContext deserializationContext) throws IOException, JsonProcessingException {
091            Unit value = new Unit();
092            switch (jsonParser.currentToken()) {
093                case VALUE_NULL:
094                    break;
095                case START_ARRAY:
096                    value.cvParameterArrayValue = jsonParser.readValueAs(new TypeReference<List<CvParameter>>() {
097                    });
098                    break;
099                case START_OBJECT:
100                    value.cvParameterValue = jsonParser.readValueAs(CvParameter.class);
101                    break;
102                default:
103                    throw new IOException("Cannot deserialize Unit");
104            }
105            return value;
106        }
107    }
108
109    static class Serializer extends JsonSerializer<Unit> {
110
111        @Override
112        public void serialize(Unit obj, JsonGenerator jsonGenerator, SerializerProvider serializerProvider) throws IOException {
113            if (obj.cvParameterValue != null) {
114                jsonGenerator.writeObject(obj.cvParameterValue);
115                return;
116            }
117            if (obj.cvParameterArrayValue != null) {
118                jsonGenerator.writeObject(obj.cvParameterArrayValue);
119                return;
120            }
121            jsonGenerator.writeNull();
122        }
123    }
124}
